# lli

> Directly execute programs from LLVM bitcode
> More information: https://www.llvm.org/docs/CommandGuide/lli.html

- Execute a bitcode or IR file:

`lli {file value: sample.ll}`

- Execute with command line arguments:

`lli {file value: sample.ll} {string value: argument1 argument2 ...}`

- Enable all optimizations:

`lli -O3 {file value: sample.ll}`

- Load a dynamic library before linking:

`lli --dlopen={string value: path/to/library.dll} {file value: sample.ll}`
